In order to use the breaklines directive in minted, you'll need to copy the latest version to your latex path.

First make a backup of your existing minted.sty:
sudo cp /usr/share/texlive/texmf-dist/tex/latex/minted/minted.sty /usr/share/texlive/texmf-dist/tex/latex/minted/minted.sty.bak

Then copy minded 2.0 in this src folder to your minted folder:
sudo cp Documents/Latex/src/minted.sty /usr/share/texlive/texmf-dist/tex/latex/minted/minted.sty

Done
